Class RDateVector

java.util.AbstractCollection<E>

uk.co.terminological.rjava.types.RVector<RDate>
uk.co.terminological.rjava.types.RDateVector
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<RDate>, Collection<RDate>, List<RDate>, RandomAccess, JNIPrimitive, RObject
public class RDateVector extends RVector<RDate> implements JNIPrimitive
Java wrapper for R vector of dates. When transferred between R and Java this uses a string format for the date. Factory methods are in RVector.
Author:
terminological
